  "What is 'probability' of an event?": "事件的可能性是什么?",
  "The percentage of the time the event has occurred in the past": "过去事件发生时间的百分比",
  "The number of outcomes in the sample space": "抽样空间结果数目",
  "A measure from 0 to 1 indicating how likely an event is to occur": "从0到1的衡量尺度,说明事件发生的可能性",
  "The count of favorable outcomes only": "仅对有利结果的计数",
  "Probability is a number between 0 and 1 (inclusive) that measures the likelihood of an event. P = 0 means impossible; P = 1 means certain.": "概率为0至1(含)之间的数字,可测量事件发生的可能性。 P = 0 表示不可能; P = 1 表示确定。",
